14
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:39,520
That they go through a period when they're out of control and behave badly.

15
00:00:39,520 --> 00:00:43,760
But, apparently, it's not their fault, at least not directly.

16
00:00:43,760 --> 00:00:45,359
So, who's fault is it?

17
00:00:45,359 --> 00:00:47,120
Our brains, apparently.

18
00:00:47,120 --> 00:00:51,280
Teenagers' brains are still developing in areas that control behaviour,

19
00:00:51,280 --> 00:00:54,480
which could mean that you can't blame them for acting the way they do.

20
