Before we find out more, let's have our question.

21
00:00:58,479 --> 00:01:03,359
There have always been teenagers, but when was the word teenager first used

22
00:01:03,359 --> 00:01:06,640
to refer to the 13 to 19-age group?

23
00:01:06,640 --> 00:01:08,640
Was it A, the 1920s?

24
00:01:08,640 --> 00:01:10,159
B, the 1930s?

25
00:01:10,159 --> 00:01:13,120
Or C, the 1950s? Any ideas, Rob?

26
00:01:13,120 --> 00:01:16,719
Well, I think it came along around the time of rock and roll,

27
00:01:16,719 --> 00:01:20,239
